to conditionally skip builds.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: ESwi0EtRnO2", "files": ["testing/mozharness/mozharness/mozilla/testing/testbase.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "ff083266e35561f5fe95ff79cad2d38c532aa708", "parents": ["ef757ca3fbfe1bb9470f6636ad22f4e6fc536fe9"], "tags": []}], "date": 1486646838, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null], "user": "cbook@mozilla.com"}, "6900": {"changesets": [{"author": "Daniel Holbert \u003cdholbert@cs.stanford.edu\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1308610 - Part 0: Remove no-longer-used mochitest helper file \"file_use_counter_svg_background.html\". r=froydnj, a=test-only\n\nThe only usages of this file were removed in an earlier bug, in this changeset:\nhttps://hg.mozilla.org/mozilla-central/rev/fe97a239ab5a\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: ERHhgJizvSE", "files": ["dom/base/test/browser.ini", "dom/base/test/file_use_counter_svg_background.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "31048f0f80cea76e509591b7d563df4838755921", "parents": ["ff083266e35561f5fe95ff79cad2d38c532aa708"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Daniel Holbert \u003cdholbert@cs.stanford.edu\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1308610 - Part 1: Remove use-counter mochitest's flaky chunk about testing counters in SVG \"list-style-image\" docs. r=froydnj, a=test-only\n\nIt's hard to predict the timing of SVG-as-an-image document teardown, for SVG\nimages used in CSS, so this piece of the test was flaky.  And anyway, we have\nother tests for use counters in SVG-as-an-image (see calls to\n\"check_use_counter_img\"), which should exercise the codepath we care about here.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: DbYWDYUOc1c", "files": ["dom/base/test/browser.ini", "dom/base/test/browser_use_counters.js", "dom/base/test/file_use_counter_svg_list_style_image.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "af422c1e8f80521e4c95a22878b0e7733d1674b0", "parents": ["31048f0f80cea76e509591b7d563df4838755921"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Johann H