02621 - Fix buggy history traversal test. r=Ms2ger, a=test-only\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: Lc7BDuxEWgY", "files": ["testing/web-platform/meta/html/browsers/browsing-the-web/history-traversal/browsing_context_name.html.ini", "testing/web-platform/tests/html/browsers/browsing-the-web/history-traversal/browsing_context_name-0.html", "testing/web-platform/tests/html/browsers/browsing-the-web/history-traversal/browsing_context_name.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "6aa6b1d56e32d15a33134ba874c9df82ea7d9b8a", "parents": ["2937b93c263751fd99f791ebfe5fbee2ec8112ea"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Brian Birtles \u003cbirtles@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1339591 - Rearrange construction order of RAII objects in SMIL code. r=mccr8, a=jcristau\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: FXFF0Phvgjj", "files": ["dom/smil/nsSMILAnimationController.cpp", "dom/smil/nsSMILInstanceTime.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "758af211353cb6c1d034b66eee910fc5bfa6531d", "parents": ["6aa6b1d56e32d15a33134ba874c9df82ea7d9b8a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mike Conley \u003cmconley@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1333223 - Add an unhandled exception handler. r=ted, a=lizzard\n\nThe exception handler calls MOZ_CRASH, which should allow\nour crash reporting infrastructure to kick in.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: FzTlXOIMzal", "files": ["toolkit/crashreporter/nsExceptionHandler.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "4ae8b06d0576da03a6474df328a86765b1f793de", "parents": ["758af211353cb6c1d034b66eee910fc5bfa6531d"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Karl Tomlinson \u003ckarlt+@karlt.net\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1331320 - Install X11 error handler through Xlib in plugin process as GTK2 does not use g_error. r=glandium, a=jcristau\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 9Io2fABc2hI", "files": ["dom/plugins/ipc/PluginModuleChild.cpp", "toolkit/xre/moz.build", "toolkit/xre/nsX11ErrorHandler.cpp", "toolkit/xre/nsX11ErrorHandler.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "50722ee37c34e9e7a33655cd88d66b3055c20efe", "parents": ["4ae8b06d0576da03a6474df328a86765b1f793de"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Karl Tomlinson \u003ckarlt+@karlt.net\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1331320 - Document requestFlakyTimeout for crashAndGetCrashServiceRecord(). r=glandium, a=jcristau\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 4l2qxJfRbkq", "files": ["dom/plugins/test/mochitest/test_CrashService_crash.html", "dom/plugins/test/mochitest/test_CrashService_hang.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "72eda3f714d5fef4f1d056209f1dc81fe93076d4", "parents": ["50722ee37c34e9e7a33655cd88d66b3055c20efe"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Karl Tomlinson \u003ckarlt+@karlt.net\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1331320 - Test that a crashreport is generated on X11 protocol error in plugin. r=glandium, a=jcristau\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: HSKgzjqRZh6", "files": ["dom/plugins/test/mochitest/mochitest.ini", "dom/plugins/test/mochitest/test_x11_error_crash.html", "dom/plugins/test/testplugin/nptest.cpp", "dom/plugins/test/testplugin/nptest_gtk2.cpp", "dom/plugins/test/testplugin/nptest_platform.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "fd7a49fdef4dd1d94b4bf9b79f9cb0bc4f951a16", "parents": ["72eda3f714d5fef4f1d056209f1dc81fe93076d4"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Karl Tomlinson \u003ckarlt+@karlt.net\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1331320 - Disable e10s browser_tab_dragdrop.js in remaining linux builds. r=mccr8, a=jcristau\n\nThe intermittent abnormal plugin exit due to bug 1237853 was not detected by\nopt builds due to the use of exit(1) and lack of leak checking (which would\nhave demonstrated bug 1309420 or bug 1239258).\n\nThe abnormal exit is now detected in opt builds also, and so this change\ndisables testing with these builds also.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: FnBGNqnJrDp", "files": ["browser/base/content/test/general/browser.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "a2d0bdf251a337954956726524b2dcb246d39c37", "parents": ["fd7a49fdef4dd1d94b4bf9b79f9cb0bc4f951a16"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Matthew Noorenberghe \u003cmozilla@noorenberghe.ca\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1332610 - Don't eagerly create Intl.DateTimeFormat in LoginManagerContextMenu.jsm. r=johannh, a=jcristau\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: IuXdWyy4C7b", "files": ["toolkit/components/passwordmgr/LoginManagerContextMenu.jsm"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5b4f6203e10adf317ab23d704049249f80e6dc3a", "parents": ["a2d0bdf251a337954956726524b2dcb246d39c37"], "tags": []}, {"author": "David Keeler \u003cdkeeler@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1339010 - Ensure pinning and CT telemetry info has been initialized. r=jcj, a=jcristau", "files": ["security/certverifier/CertVerifier.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "bb25cae5b8f7a8d2a116af55cf6c4e6ab0ee924c", "parents": ["5b4f6203e10adf317ab23d704049249f80e6dc3a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Kris Maglione \u003cmaglione.k@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1339483 - Fix tab frame lookup performance issues. r=mossop, a=jcristau\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: Fvx1J8bpzGg", "files": ["addon-sdk/source/lib/sdk/remote/child.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "0c1e68e123374a757dc2ece8d100ddd1d7711842", "parents": ["bb25cae5b8f7a8d2a116af55cf6c4e6ab0ee924c"], "tags": []}, {"author": "JW Wang \u003cjwwang@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1339677 - Add sanity checks to debug MozPromise crashes. r=gerald, a=lizzard\n\nBug 1339677. Part 1 - assert DoResolveOrReject() is called on the target thread and use stronger assertions. r=gerald\nBug 1339677. Part 2 - some code cleanup and remove unnecessary scope qualifiers. r=gerald\nBug 1339677. Part 3 - add some sanity checks. r=gerald\nBug 1339677. Part 4 - check if mMutex.mLock is tampered. r=gerald", "files": ["xpcom/glue/Mutex.h", "xpcom/threads/MozPromise.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "n